OL,5,G0100 Outback Truckers
OL,6,     FThe stakes are high as Danyelle
OL,7,     Fand Anthony Haigh battle extreme
OL,8,     Fheat and dust drilling in search
OL,9,     Fof life giving water for one of
OL,10,     Fthe most remote cattle stations in
OL,11,     FAustralia.
OL,12,G0200 Trucking Hell
